  </developer>
  <supports>
    <control>pointing</control>
    <control>keyboard</control>
    <control>touch</control>
  </supports>
  <description>
    <p>yeTTY is an open source application for embedded developers to
    view logs from serial port.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Text highlighting</li>
      <li>Auto reconnection</li>
      <li>Audio alert on string match</li>
      <li>Long term run mode</li>
      <li>Suspend during flashing</li>
      <li>Auto baud rate detection</li>
      <li>Auto background color change on microcontroller reset</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
